    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained over the years. The engine is reliable and provides a smooth driving experience, while the transmission shifts cleanly through all gears. The interior is clean with only minor signs of wear, and the exterior paint retains a nice shine despite a few small blemishes from regular use. It\u2019s a dependable car that\u2019s ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
